{"tid":1302680,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"呀媽以為我夠分入左HKU ，點算好","createTime":"2019-07-10T04:42:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T06:16:00.000Z","uid":133519,"like":4,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"06e43d424f65d14c88e5514303753f7ecb8138dd","tid":1302680,"uid":133519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T04:42:11.000Z","msg":"是咁的 <br />\n<br />\n我今年考dse，今日放榜 <br />\n我考得唔係太好，又怕呀媽擔心 <br />\n呀媽一生人既夢想佢個仔我入大學 <br />\n因為佢d親戚街坊都無仔女入到U <br />\n<br />\n今日一早番左屋企時，呀媽係咁問我成績點，夠唔夠分, 可以入邊間U <br />\n我心情唔好，是撚但但同呀媽佢講我去讀藥劑， <br />\n之後請入房訓較(尋晚通左頂) <br />\n<br />\n我起左身，屙完屎之後出黎 <br />\n發現成家人都好開心，呀爸呀媽叫撚晒佢d親戚姑嫂話今晚出黎食飯 <br />\n同個仔慶祝入到HKU讀藥劑 <br />\n<br />\n依個時候先知大撚獲 <br />\n我其實係去報IVE讀藥劑 <br />\n唔撚知邊個親戚街坊話係香港既大學，只有HKU有藥劑讀 <br />\n所以呀媽以為我夠分入左HKU <br />\n<br />\n屌你 <br />\n我而家點做好......... <br />\n<br />\n點算好"},{"pid":"85f3fbe7ca9e246a32087417ec279310afd53ca7","tid":1302680,"uid":102700,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T04:43:19.000Z","msg":"舊聞<br />\n上一頁"},{"pid":"ff84b250853956ad5c16823c311031d910df5837","tid":1302680,"uid":107216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T05:08:55.000Z","msg":"你係咪覺得好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我睇到識背啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34b291f5678f95df67dc9eecfc82357fa0a9be19","tid":1302680,"uid":246417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T05:40:15.000Z","msg":"又嚟"},{"pid":"e52a2de90bcc6e5d242b20718ae77dc0f8c95fee","tid":1302680,"uid":35315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T05:55:32.000Z","msg":"好撚悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"585075d3b8c9e56e76aee9a93aff50b5c0665877","tid":1302680,"uid":200145,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ff84b250853956ad5c16823c311031d910df5837","tid":1302680,"uid":107216,"lik